value: Breeds in North America east of the Cascades and Sierra Nevada from Great Slave Lake and Lake Winnipeg (rarely to the Gulf of St. Lawrence and northern New England) south to Nevada, New Mexico and Louisiana. Winters south over Mexico, Central America and the West Indies to north- ern South America (Peru on the west and Cayenne on the northeast).
